        {
            "title": "美國新屋開工量飆升至2024年12月以來的最高水平 高於預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"US Census Bureau, Department of Housing and Urban Development\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"705\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sticKWhy69P1xC3wyXA7WA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcwNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/d9d17ff8967b2e6582b2e203f91c40c7\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">US Census Bureau, Department of Housing and Urban Development</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國新屋建設在3月份升至一年多來最高水平。儘管住房負擔能力擔憂持續存在，但住宅建築商仍提高了施工量。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國普查局周三公佈的數據顯示，3月份新屋開工數成長10.8%，折合年率為150萬套，為2024年12月以來最高水平。這一數據高於彭博新聞社調查中所有經濟學家的預估。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"705\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bNfzbXY_cqqMOzsAyJDO0Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcwNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5514930729b2c0325d489180549b043c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月份新建獨棟住宅開工數成長9.7%，折合年率為103萬套，而多戶住宅開工數也有所上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周三這份報告表明，隨著建築商繼續提供銷售激勵以吸引潛在買家入市，住宅建設開始趨於穩定。但伊朗戰爭加劇了經濟不確定性，不僅推高了材料成本，也推高了抵押貸款利率。一項衡量住宅建築商信心的指標在4月份跌至7個月低點。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-363a8ee1-98bd-3ad5-af54-08e4913aedb8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報告顯示，作為未來建築活動先行指標的建築許可在3月份降至折合年率137萬套，為8月份以來最低水平。獨棟住宅建築許可下降3.8%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國四大地區的新屋開工數均有所增加，其中東北部地區增幅領先。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Housing Starts Surge to Highest Level Since December 2024 (3)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
