        {
            "title": "通用動力、ADP盤前上漲;SoFi Technologies下滑",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AYTuDsnN.P0A4xGITM_bHw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/General-Dynamics-_M_1440049738.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 美國股指期貨週三幾乎持平,市場�靜待今年迄今為止最繁忙的交易日之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"美國東部時間\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:美國東部時間;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/美國東部時間\">美國東部時間</a>上午06:58(北京時間18:58),道瓊斯期貨合約基本持平,標普500期貨上漲5點或0.1%,納斯達克100期貨攀升92點或0.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以下是今日盤前美股最大的波動股:</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Alphabet、Microsoft、Amazon和Meta均小幅下跌。這些大型科技巨頭將在收盤後公布財報,投資者期待這些公司就其大規模人工智能支出計劃提供最新進展。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">通用動力公司(General Dynamics Corporation)股價攀升,這家航空航天和國防公司第一季度營收增長10%。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自動數據處理公司(Automatic Data Processing)上調全年調整後利潤預測,推動該公司股價走高。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">再生元製藥(Regeneron Pharmaceuticals)小幅下跌,儘管該集團公布的第一季度利潤和營收好於預期,主要得益於其濕疹藥物Dupixent的強勁需求。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Phillips 66股價上漲,這家美國下游能源供應商第一季度調整後每股收益高於預期。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Penske股價小幅上揚,這家美國汽車和卡車零售商第一季度營收好於預期。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">數字金融服務公司SoFi大幅下挫,儘管該公司第一季度利潤翻倍,創紀錄的貸款發放和會員增長。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Tradeweb股價下跌,這家電子交易平台表示其全年調整後費用預期將趨向11億美元至11.6億美元區間的上半部分。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hayward Holdings小幅下滑,儘管這家專業水管理公司第一財季銷售額和調整後攤薄每股收益均超出預期。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Scotts Miracle-Gro大漲,這家美國草坪和園藝公司調整後核心收益高於預期。</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Virtu Financial股價上漲,這家電子交易公司季度調整後淨利潤飆升71%,超出預期。</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
