        {
            "title": "短炒波士｜港股再下行空間不大 分析個股表現｜Ringo",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"426\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/c_G2m4fOwFHraCEJibxRIQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/c13fa68616dc9546a7f8d1765e77a2ca\" width=\"640\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">港股連續兩個交易日向下，惟料短線下行空間不大，跌至25,400點可有支持。惟在本月餘下兩個交易日也預期難會出現大幅上升，估計恒指本月結算價介乎25,700點至25,800點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">騰訊（700）失守早前提及的支持位480元，故預期股價有機會繼續向下，下一支持位在460元。中資科技龍頭股在AI方面的發展明顯較國際同業落後，若繼續「食老本」，股價整體表現仍只會易跌難升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">受惠AI基建熱潮對覆銅板需求大增的建滔積層板（1888），股價繼續破頂。破頂股無須估頂，其上行動能有力帶領股價再次破頂，若股價回調，可視32.5元為止賺位。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c323f7a0-97bd-3b52-9c93-563d50f697e6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國宏橋（1378）計劃溢價發行可換股債券，股價挫近半成。該股今年曾3次上破40元不果而造成三頂局面，但回調至30元便有支持，預期股價會繼續在30元至40元之間上落，投資者可考慮在跌至30元附近持反彈，升近40元便食糊。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">寧德時代（3750）折讓7%配股集資，導致股價周二亦跌約7%。寧德時代由3月初約500元炒至近期約700元的水平，便於高位抽水配股。此種炒高配股的做法往往不利股價短期表現，故現時不應急於撈底，待跌至570元至580元才吸納更合適。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國產芯片股近日表現亮麗，但中芯國際（981）已升至70元的阻力位，在低位已買入的投資者可考慮先行獲利。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Ringo<br/>資深投資者<br/>註：專欄作家言論不代表本網立場</strong></p><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":0,\"yLinkElement\":\"img\"}' data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://signup.hkiei.com/ringo_webinar_bossmind\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"686\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ImrasCUjN02l5wpgg5PUdQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/f52012128630469615370091d56ff897\" width=\"960\"/></div></a></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9F%AD%E7%82%92%E6%B3%A2%E5%A3%AB-%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E5%86%8D%E4%B8%8B%E8%A1%8C%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%A7-%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%80%8B%E8%82%A1%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE-ringo-123000311.html",
